  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Mercy in Action</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The Iglesia Luterana Confesional de Chile (ILC-Chile) has developed a plan for &quot;Mercy in Action&quot; through which they will provide rehabilitative activities in the Bethesda Care/Support Center in Santiago; after school programs and family workshops in Community Centers in Valparaiso and Constitucion. ILC-Chile will finalize the center for disabled youth and adults in Santiago and create spaces for children and families suffering from the trauma and loss from devastating fires of 2014 in Valparaiso and the devastating earthquake and tsunami in La Constitucion.</narrative>
  </description>
